\f0\fs24 \cf0 This Product Requirements Document (PRD) outlines the design for the\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Smart Audio Bridge
\f0\b0 , a custom hardware/software solution that functions as a Bluetooth recorder with passthrough capability. It uses a\

\f1\b Raspberry Pi Zero 2W\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 to capture phone audio by emulating a headset, while allowing for local storage and automated offloading for AI transcription.\
Product Requirements Document (PRD): Smart Audio Bridge v1.0\
1. Executive Summary\
The\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Smart Audio Bridge\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 is a portable device that acts as a "man-in-the-middle" between a primary smartphone and a user's wired headset. It emulates a Bluetooth Hands-Free Profile (HFP) headset to record both sides of a phone conversation while allowing the user to communicate through a wired high-quality cardioid microphone and earpiece. Recorded data is stored locally and automatically uploaded to a primary computer for AI transcription via a local 
\f1\b OpenAI Whisper
\f0\b0  model.\
2. Product Objectives\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Privacy-First Recording:
\f0\b0  Ensure all data remains local until moved to the user's primary workstation.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Open Workflow Integration:
\f0\b0  Provide a system that allows developers to access raw audio via standard protocols (SSH/SFTP), bypassing closed proprietary ecosystems.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}High-Fidelity Capture:
\f0\b0  Use professional-grade wired microphones to ensure the highest possible transcription accuracy.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Automated Offloading:
\f0\b0  Create a "set and forget" experience where the device syncs files whenever the primary computer's network is reachable.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 3. Scope & Phases\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}v1.0 (Current):
\f0\b0  USB-C audio interface for input/output. Focus on software routing and automated syncing.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}v2.0 (Future):
\f0\b0  GPIO-based I2S audio input/output to achieve near-zero latency and a smaller physical footprint.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
