5. Functional Requirements\
5.1 Bluetooth Role Emulation\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The device must appear as a 
